secubox-admin (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release - System administration module.
  * FastAPI backend with psutil-based system monitoring.
  * Endpoints: status, services, logs, storage, processes, updates.
  * Service control: start, stop, restart systemd units.
  * System actions: reboot, shutdown with confirmation.
  * APT updates: check and run system upgrades.
  * Audit logging for all administrative actions (CSPN compliant).
  * P31 Phosphor light theme frontend with orange accent.
  * Tabs: Overview, Services, Logs, Storage, Processes, Updates.

 -- Gerald KERMA <devel@cybermind.fr>  Fri, 04 Apr 2026 16:00:00 +0200
